room_title: Escape room "Area 53: Lunar Lockdown" by Escape Room Tucson in Tucson
room_description: We’ve all heard of Area 51, but no one knows about Area 53! Area 53 is a top-secret government facility on the moon that is used for alien experiments. We’ve learned that a test subject has escaped containment in the Dark Sector. The alert sirens sounded off and the station went on lockdown. The lead scientist, Dr. Bishop, is now missing. Your team is being sent in to contain the situation and get back to earth within 60 minutes.
